#: 2020-07-17-pandemics-environment.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "1. Pandemics Start with Wild Animals"
msgstr "1. Les pandémies commencent avec les animaux sauvages"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-17-pandemics-environment.md:26
msgid ""
"![sick pangolin in a small cage, coughing "
"COVID-19](/assets/uploads/pangolin-cough.png)  ﻿"
msgstr ""
"![sick pangolin in a small cage, coughing COVID-19](/assets/uploads/pangolin-"
